A dramatic aerial view of a vast global network visualization at dusk, showing glowing orange and amber data streams flowing between a central crystalline server tower and dozens of smaller translucent nodes scattered across a stylized dark world map. The streams split and merge like rivers of light, with one prominent golden pathway arcing from a sleek modern data center building toward a constellation of floating geometric shapes representing edge locations. The scene has a cinematic quality with deep blue shadows, warm orange highlights, and subtle cloud formations below, suggesting the infrastructure exists in the stratosphere. Photorealistic rendering with slight stylization, moody lighting reminiscent of blade runner cinematography.
